snippet.title: Ultima 4 gameplay (PC Game, 1985)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Ultima 4 (aka ultima iv: quest of the avatar), Dos PC game produced by ORIGIN Systems in 1985 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/ultima-4/785/
Watching the intro and exploring in this classic fantasy adventure.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
